All universities will be completing the 2020 academic year by mid-March. That's the assurance from the Higher Education Ministry. Shahan Ramkissoon spoke to Deputy Higher Education Minister Buti Manamela. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 PRETORIA - Higher Education Minister, Blade Nzimande says universities will complete the 2020 academic year in March next year. He made the announcement during a media briefing on Thursday. READ: WATCH: Nzimande speaks on measures to save academic year Nzimande announced further measures his department will implement to curb the spread of COVID-19. For more, watch the interview above